title: Razer Huntsman Elite Gaming Keyboard - Is It REALLY Worth $200?
description: Razer has launched a brand new mechanical keyboard called the Huntsman Elite which uses their advanced purple optomechanical switches and costs a cool $200. It also features the new Synapse 3. That price alone makes the Huntsman one of the most expensive gaming keyboards on the market but does its performance and speed live up to such a high price point?
